fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "Contributing.html#external-dependencies", "fragment": "External dependencies \nThe goal of Meson is to be as easily usable as possible. The user experience should be get Python3 and Ninja run even on Windows. Unfortunately this means that we can t have dependencies on projects outside of Python s standard library. This applies only to core functionality though. For additional helper programs etc the use of external dependencies may be ok. If you feel that you are dealing with this kind of case please contact the developers first with your use case. \n"});